{"tid":1913594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利疫情蔓延政府下令禁止接吻 市民：病毒不可怕，死了都要親","createTime":"2020-03-07T02:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:17:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b149673026a9af400ce1122b22bb15db4d58ec9","tid":1913594,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:33:08.000Z","msg":"當地時間3月5日，世衛組織發佈最新一期新冠肺炎情況每日報告。截至當地時間3月5日18時，意大利單日新增新冠肺炎病例769例，新增數爲全球最多。日前，意大利總理孔特緊急頒佈了一項新的法令，其中的禁令除了關閉電影院和劇院外，還包括禁止接吻等意大利傳統問候方式。但是街頭的市民表示，病毒並不能阻止接吻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/212/w550h462/20200307/ed9a-iqmtvwv5122343.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fnews%2Ftransform%2F212%2Fw550h462%2F20200307%2Fed9a-iqmtvwv5122343.png&h=ef55bd5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.us.sina.com/bg/international/sinacn/2020-03-06/detail-ifzufvmq2800951.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.us.sina.com%2Fbg%2Finternational%2Fsinacn%2F2020-03-06%2Fdetail-ifzufvmq2800951.shtml&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=156e5ee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.us.sina.com/bg/international/sinacn/2020-03-06/detail-ifzufvmq2800951.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"bd11c88cdffd902439d0fea65dcf12d3970c402a","tid":1913594,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"死了都要愛～"},{"pid":"a012e04a818c2966e51255e66457a3e933a630ff","tid":1913594,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"香港都有叫人唔好嘴自己隻狗，班狗佬都唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由佢死啦"},{"pid":"a3548d477c2d97ceea610677ac9b425bb2fe86b0","tid":1913594,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7fdbe54d21809e3385532cf2d204d914b746fef","tid":1913594,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:35:21.0